OL,3,CVisually impaired mum told she 'should
OL,4,Cnot have kids' in disability hate crime
OL,6,FA mother with a disability says she
OL,7,Fhas been told she "shouldn't be having
OL,8,Fa kid" while travelling home on the
OL,9,Fbus from a soft play area with her son.
OL,11,FSamantha Ralfe, and her husband Martin
OL,12,FRalfe live in St Helens, both living
OL,13,Fwith a visual impairment.
OL,15,FThe couple raise awareness on TikTok
OL,16,Fabout having a disability while
OL,17,Fbringing up their three-year-old boy
OL,18,FLeo.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
