OL,3,CVisually impaired mum told she 'should
OL,4,Cnot have kids' in disability hate crime
OL,6,FSam says she often experiences hate
OL,7,Fonline and abuse in public, she said:
OL,8,F"Myself and Leo, and Bailey, my guide
OL,9,Fdog, were on the bus just coming home
OL,10,Ffrom a soft play... and I could hear
OL,11,Fsome woman behind saying that 'oh look
OL,12,Fshe's disabled, she shouldn't be
OL,13,Fhaving a kid'.
OL,15,F"There were quite nasty words that
OL,16,Fwere said, and after awhile it was
OL,17,Fjust a case of turning around and
OL,18,Fsaying 'can you stop, because you
OL,19,Fdon't understand.' She called me a
OL,20,Fsp****c.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
