OL,3,CVisually impaired mum told she 'should
OL,4,Cnot have kids' in disability hate crime
OL,6,F"There was no point me reporting it to
OL,7,Fanyone, because no one's going to do
OL,8,Fanything. No one would of stuck up for
OL,9,Fme and said 'yes, I did hear that'."
OL,11,FAlthough Sam tries to not let the hate
OL,12,Ftowards her impairment effect her,
OL,13,Fthere are times when it does create
OL,14,Fdoubt.
OL,16,FShe said: "In the moment once your
OL,17,Fbusy looking after your child and your
OL,18,Fguide dog, you just kind of let it go
OL,19,Fover your head, you don't really care.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
