OL,3,CVisually impaired mum told she 'should
OL,4,Cnot have kids' in disability hate crime
OL,6,F"But it's when your sat at home just
OL,7,Fbefore you go to sleep, you sit there
OL,8,Fand think about the day and it does
OL,9,Fget to you.
OL,11,F"Later on you do think, are they
OL,12,Fright? Am I the one in the wrong? Am I
OL,13,Fthe bad person for doing this? But you
OL,14,Fjust have to let it go the best you
OL,15,Fcan."
OL,17,FDisability hate crime is defined as
OL,18,Fdiscrimination motivated by a person's
OL,19,Fdisability.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
