OL,3,CVisually impaired mum told she 'should
OL,4,Cnot have kids' in disability hate crime
OL,6,FRachel Ruffle, from Sale, who became a
OL,7,Fwheelchair user after a spinal cord
OL,8,Finjury, has a 14-year-old daughter
OL,9,Fcalled Amelie.
OL,11,FShe believes people do not pair
OL,12,Fdisability and parenting together.
OL,14,F"When she was very little I think that
OL,15,Fwas the hardest bit," she said.
OL,17,F"She ran off on me once in the
OL,18,FTrafford Centre, oh it was a
OL,19,Fnightmare, because I can't chase her,
OL,20,FI can't bring her back.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
