OL,3,CVisually impaired mum told she 'should
OL,4,Cnot have kids' in disability hate crime
OL,6,F"Somebody came up to me and said
OL,7,F'well, if you can't chase after your
OL,8,Fchild then you really shouldn't have
OL,9,Fher here.'
OL,11,F"Comments like that sometimes makes
OL,12,Fyou question yourself, but it also
OL,13,Fmakes you question yourself when your
OL,14,Fkid runs off and you know you can't
OL,15,Fgrab them, that kind of sows a seed of
OL,16,Fdoubt in your head."
